<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玉帝坐在凌霄宝殿的宝座上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>信使跑进了宝殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“东海龙王有事求见。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让他进来。”玉帝说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>龙王走进来，向玉帝行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下，我要告状。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孙悟空去我的龙宫要求我给他兵器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他实在太过分了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>又一个信使走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阎王有事求见，陛下。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阎王走进来行了礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有个叫孙悟空的猴子把他的名字从生死簿里划去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我请求您惩罚他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玉帝摸了摸下巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个孙悟空是谁？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他为什么有那么大的本事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天将走上前来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空就是三百年前出生的那只石猴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不知道他是如何有这般本事的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我记得他。”玉帝说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不管他有多大本事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在人间惹了太多麻烦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>召集天兵天将，下界去花果山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103015</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>给我把孙悟空抓来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103016</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太白金星走上前来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下！”太白金星说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我们可以在天庭给那孙悟空一个工作。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玉帝扬起了眉毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们为什么要这么做？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果他来了天庭，我们就可以盯着他了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太白金星说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“想让他不惹麻烦就会是件很容易的事情了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“非常好。”玉帝说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就请孙悟空来天庭吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他就负责看管蟠桃园。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空正在给他的孩儿们讲在幽冥界的经历。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我把我的名字划掉后，”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我把你们所有的名字也都划掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在我们都可以长生不老了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猴子们欢呼起来。“美猴王万岁！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空注意到一个神仙站在了他们旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抽出了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182051</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是太白金星。”那个神仙说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是来帮玉帝送信儿给你的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189893</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他希望你来天庭生活。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最后，他还是得邀请我去嘛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空走进凌霄宝殿后，并没有行礼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你应该向玉帝行礼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212091</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太白金星轻声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我和他一样强大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他该向我行礼才对！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除了玉帝，殿上的每个人都倒吸了一口冷气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228971</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看着玉帝：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你请我来，我很高兴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237442</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想，你最终还是意识到了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我应该在这天庭里生活。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“注意你的言语。”太白金星说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玉帝看了看太白金星，然后笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空刚来，他不行礼可以理解。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254168</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着孙悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我让你负责蟠桃园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>以后，天庭就是你的家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我希望你不要再惹任何麻烦了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听上去不错！”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，一个园丁就领着悟空去了蟠桃园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里的每根树枝上都挂满了闪闪发光的桃子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这园里的桃子可不像人间的桃子。”园丁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里的桃子要几千年才成熟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>任何人只要咬上一口这桃子便可长生不老。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天早上，悟空都在蟠桃园里查看桃树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他工作的时候非常严肃认真。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319186</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这些桃子看上去很好吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空有一天想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个园丁都没看到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我可以吃一个。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>